sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Start as Opportunity change
  participant Bpmn as Maestro BPMN
  participant Agent as Coded Agents
  participant Robot as WaitDecision Robot
  participant Hitl as AWS Lambda HITL bridge
  participant Outlook as Outlook
  participant Slack as Slack
  participant AC as Action Center
  participant Approver as Approver
  participant Log as Data Fabric

  Start->>Bpmn: Start instance (Salesforce payload)
  Bpmn->>Agent: plan (risk score + LLM rationale + chain)
  Agent-->>Bpmn: disposition, recommendation, approver chain
  alt disposition == auto_approve
    Bpmn->>Log: Record auto_approved
  else disposition == needs_approval
    loop per approver in chain
      Bpmn->>Agent: render (approval payload)
      Bpmn->>Robot: create approval (suspend via Persistence)
      Robot->>Hitl: POST /api/v1/approvals (mint response token)
      Robot->>Outlook: send Adaptive Card
      Robot->>Slack: send Block Kit DM
      Robot->>AC: create external task (wait for task)
      Approver->>Outlook: click Approve / Reject
      Approver-->>AC: or decide in Action Center
      Hitl-->>Robot: decision via token callback
      Robot-->>Bpmn: resume, return out_Decision
      Bpmn->>Agent: process_response (interpret decision)
      note over Bpmn: rejection short-circuits remaining chain
    end
    Bpmn->>Slack: notify requester (DM)
    Bpmn->>Outlook: notify requester (summary)
    Bpmn->>Log: record agent rec vs each human decision
  end
